These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, mirinda, iced-tea
3 different pets are kept: bird, ferret, rat
1. the owner of the rat is somewhere between the person drinking hot-chocolate and the owner of the ferret##7
2. the owner of the bird is somewhere to the right of the owner of the ferret##5
3. the person drinking mirinda is somewhere to the right of the owner of the ferret##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |   3   |
| Beverage   | iced-tea | mirinda | hot-chocolate |
| Pet           | ferret  | rat     | bird  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-2::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: adventure, disaster, animation
The people use 3 different means of transport: subway, tram, van
1. the person driving the subway is in an odd position##4
2. the person watching adventure movies is somewhere between the person watching animation movies and the person driving the tram##7
3. the person driving the subway is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |   3    |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster | adventure | animation |
| Transport     | tram       | van     | subway |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-3::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: purple, ivory, blue
The people use 3 different means of transport: roller, subway, train
1. the person driving the subway is somewhere between the person who likes purple and the person driving the roller##7
2. the person driving the train is on the left of the person who likes ivory##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2    |   3    |
| Color    | purple | ivory | blue  |
| Transport   | train  | subway  | roller |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-4::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  project-manager, scientist, teacher
3 different games are played: whist, domino, monopoly
1. the project-manager is somewhere between the person playing monopoly and the scientist##7
2. the person playing domino is not the project-manager##6
3. the person playing monopoly is somewhere to the right of the person playing domino##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |        2        |      3      |
| Job           | scientist | project-manager | teacher     |
| Game   | domino    | whist          | monopoly |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-5::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: green, orange, turquise
The people use 3 different means of transport: motorbike, quad-bike, skateboard
1. the person driving the quad-bike is somewhere between the person driving the skateboard and the person who likes orange##7
2. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the person who likes turquise##1
3. the person who likes orange is on the left or right of the person driving the quad-bike##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3     |
| Color   | green      | turquise     | orange   |
| Transport     | skateboard | quad-bike | motorbike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-6::.
There 3 different types of food: asparagus, eggplant, zucchini
There are 3 different nationalities: colombian, japanese, pakistani
1. the colombian is on the left or right of the japanese##3
2. the japanese is somewhere to the left of the colombian##5
3. the person eating eggplant is on the right of the pakistani##1
4. the person eating eggplant is somewhere between the pakistani and the person eating asparagus##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3     |
| Food   | zucchini    | eggplant     | asparagus     |
| Nationality   | pakistani | japanese | colombian |

