.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-7::.
3 different pets are kept: goat, goldfish, rat
There 3 different types of food: plum, broccoli, cucumber
1. the person eating cucumber is on the right of the person eating plum##1
2. the person eating cucumber is somewhere between the owner of the goat and the person eating plum##7
3. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the owner of the rat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |       2       |     3      |
| Pet     | rat       | goldfish      | goat       |
| Food   | plum | cucumber | broccoli |

