There are 3 different favourite beverages: tea, 7up, milk
1. the person drinking milk is on the left or right of the doctor##3
2. the person drinking tea is somewhere between the person drinking milk and the electrician##7
3. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the doctor##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2    |      3      |
| Job           | entrepreneur | doctor  | electrician |
| Beverage   | milk      | tea | 7up      |

