.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-10::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: coffee, milk, sprite
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, siglo, game
1. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
2. the game-smoker is the person drinking milk##1
3. the person drinking sprite is somewhere between the person drinking milk and the siglo-smoker##7

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Beverage   | milk   | sprite    | coffee |
| Cigar      | game | tiparillo | siglo |

