2. the owner of the turtle is somewhere between the owner of the rat and the person eating lemon##7
3. the person eating onion is somewhere to the right of the owner of the turtle##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |     3     |
| Food          | lemon  | plum       | onion     |
| Pet   | cat | turtle | rat |

