2. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
3. the person who likes lilac is somewhere between the person who likes yellow and the person drinking cola##7
4. the person drinking cola is on the left or right of the person who likes lilac##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |  3   |
| Beverage      | coffee     | iced-tea | cola |
