.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-15::.
There 3 different types of food: artichoke, cherry, cranberry
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: cricket, swimming, water-polo
1. the person eating artichoke is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1
2. the person who's sport is water-polo is somewhere between the person eating cranberry and the person who's sport is swimming##7
3. the person eating cranberry is on the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |    3     |
| Food     | cranberry  | artichoke       | cherry    |
| Sport   | cricket | water-polo | swimming |

