.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-16::.
House: townhouse, farmhouse, victorian
There are 3 different nationalities: malaysian, pakistani, thai
1. the townhouse house is somewhere to the right of the victorian house##5
2. the victorian house is the victorian house##1
3. the farmhouse house is somewhere between the thai and the malaysian##7
4. the malaysian is the townhouse house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3     |
| House          | victorian | farmhouse     | townhouse   |
| Nationality   | thai   | pakistani | malaysian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-17::.
There are 3 different nationalities: french, indonesian, malaysian
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: may, october, april
1. the indonesian is in an even position##4
2. the indonesian is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in october##5
3. the person who's birthday is in april is somewhere between the french and the person who's birthday is in may##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3     |
| Nationality   | french   | indonesian | malaysian |
| Birthday         | october | april | may |

