2. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the person driving the trike##1
3. the person driving the trike is somewhere between the person driving the airplane and the person who's hobby is baking##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2   |  3  |
| Hobby   | traveling     | woodworking | baking |
| Transport     | airplane | trike | van |

