.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-20::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, mirinda, tea
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: swisher, alhambra, blend
1. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the swisher-smoker##1
2. the person drinking tea is somewhere between the person drinking mirinda and the alhambra-smoker##7
3. the person drinking tea is somewhere to the left of the alhambra-smoker##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1       |    2    |      3      |
| Beverage   | mirinda      | tea     | almond-milk |
| Cigar        | blend | swisher | alhambra    |

 